      "image": "https://book-pic.webnovel.com/bookcover/35671209300388905?imageMogr2/thumbnail/600x&imageId=1776753697934",
      "description": "Sometimes the Moon Goddess breaks one bond to make room for something stronger.\n\"I reject you, Sophie. This pack needs a Luna who knows her place. And you've always been too much, Sophie.\" Those words shattered my world, but they were only the beginning.\nOne night, Sophie Turner lost everything: her mate, her pack, and her future.\nRejected by her destined mate and betrayed by her pack, the fierce Luna warrior finds herself drowning her sorrows at a human bar. That's where she meets the mysterious Christian Knight.\nHe's dangerously handsome, lethally powerful, and the Alpha of a rival pack. But as Sophie starts her new life at Knight Industries, she realizes the terrifying truth:\nThe man who rules the boardroom is the same man who is claimed by her soul.\n\"She was a discard,\" my ex-mate spat, \"a Beta who wasn't enough.\"\nChristian's growl vibrated through the room, his eyes turning a lethal gold. \"Then you're a fool. She was never meant to be a Beta. She was born to be my Queen.\"",
